  "title": "✨🌟IMMEDIATE Brand Crew/Promoter !!!🌟 ✨",
  "description": "<p>Brand Promoting Crew – Be the Voice, Vibe & Vision of Our Events! ✨</p><p><br /></p><p>IMMEDIATE HIRING!!</p><p><br /></p><p>Attractive weekly pay: $600-$1000</p><p>Work Schedule: 5-5.5 days per week</p><p>Shift: 08:30 AM - 5 PM/ 12:30 PM - 9 PM</p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p><br /></p><p>Interact and engage with customers at event booths</p><p>Handle customer questions and provide assistance</p><p>Support with on-site event operations and tasks</p><p>Join our Events Marketing team and become the heartbeat of major campaigns and on-ground brand experiences! In this role, you’ll turn ideas into excitement, audiences into fans, and events into moments people remember.</p><p><br /></p><p>If you’re creative, energetic, and love connecting brands with people in fresh, engaging ways — this is where you shine.</p><p><br /></p><p>What You’ll Do:</p><p><br /></p><p>Drive event awareness through social media, outreach, and creative marketing tactics</p><p>Represent the brand on-site with confidence and charisma</p><p>Plan and execute marketing activities that attract crowds and boost engagement</p><p>Build hype through content creation, promotions, and on-ground interactions</p><p>Analyse audience behaviour to improve future events and campaigns</p><p>Who You Are:</p><p><br /></p><p>Join us and turn every event into a story worth sharing — where your creativity brings brands to life.</p>",
